  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个甘特图来展示RR调度在Q=4ms时间片下的执行过程，时间范围是16到34毫秒。这个场景涉及三个进程：P1是单KLT，P2有两个KLT，P3是KLT加ULT的混合模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "16-34ms",
        "q=4ms",
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "klt",
        "klt+ult"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，时间轴用毫秒显示。P1只有一个内核线程，P2有两个内核线程可以并行，P3是混合线程模型。那P1的T1在这个时间段内是怎么执行的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "klt",
        "t1 exec",
        "t1 exec2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P1的T1分两段执行：第一段从16ms开始到20ms，然后被抢占；等到26ms再次获得CPU，执行到30ms。所以P1部分要有两个active状态的任务条，分别标注为T1_exec和T1_exec2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "t1 exec",
        "t1 exec2",
        "16",
        "20",
        "26",
        "30"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，P1部分已经加上两个active任务条，时间分别是16-20和26-30。现在看P2，你说有两个KLT，那T1和T2怎么分配时间片？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "2 klt",
        "t1 exec",
        "t2 exec"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P2的T1在20ms开始执行，到24ms结束。然后T2从30ms执行到34ms。注意T1还有一段最终执行从34ms到38ms，虽然超出34ms范围也要标出来。另外T2在16ms有个I/O完成的里程碑事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p2",
        "t1 exec",
        "t2 exec",
        "t1 final",
        "t2 io end",
        "20",
        "24",
        "30",
        "34",
        "38",
        "16"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "P2部分我加了T1_exec（20-24）、T2_exec（30-34）、T1_final（34-38），还有16ms的I/O里程碑。P3的KLT+ULT混合模式怎么体现？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p2",
        "t1 exec",
        "t2 exec",
        "t1 final",
        "t2 io end",
        "milestone",
        "p3",
        "klt+ult"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P3的T1在24-26ms执行。关键是T2，由于ULT在用户态完成，不占用内核调度，所以标为done状态，时间也是24-26ms，和T1重叠。这体现了ULT的轻量级特性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p3",
        "t1 exec",
        "t2 complete",
        "done",
        "24",
        "26",
        "klt+ult"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P3部分已添加，T1_exec是active状态24-26，T2_complete是done状态24-26。整体结构完成了，需要调整视觉样式吗？比如用深色主题配合特定的主色调？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p3",
        "t1 exec",
        "t2 complete",
        "active",
        "done",
        "primarycol",
        "linecol"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，用base主题，主色用#5a6c7d这种偏灰蓝的色调，边框深一点用#34495e，文字用#2c3e50，连线用#7f8c8d。整体要专业简洁的风格。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "primarycol",
